    "Set sector at report level. Set sub_sector at report or chapter level.",
    "A report may carry multiple sub_sector values but typically one sector.",
    "Civil is the residual sector — if a domain does not fit Commercial, Revenue, Defence, Telecom, or Railways, it belongs under Civil.",
